### 请求 /cps/rebate-record/page 接口 => 成功
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/rebate-record/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/rebate-record/page 接口 => 按会员筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/rebate-record/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&memberId=1001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/rebate-record/page 接口 => 按平台+状态筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/rebate-record/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&platformCode=taobao&rebateStatus=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/rebate-record/page 接口 => 按时间段筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/rebate-record/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&createTime[0]=2026-01-01 00:00:00&createTime[1]=2026-12-31 23:59:59
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/rebate-record/get 接口 => 成功
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/rebate-record/get?id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/rebate-record/reverse 接口 => 成功（触发退款回扣）
POST {{baseUrl}}/cps/rebate-record/reverse?orderId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}
